reviews.review_text: Nice Auds. Just streamed a few songs on these three Greeks very nice sounding auds.

Great sound/show This is really a top-notch AUD. Jerry's leads are crispy. Tiger never sounded better than in '83-'86. Very cool version of "Ramble on Rose." Classic Greek show. They never played a mediocre show at this venue.
